Current Status Overview
Completed Deliverables
Phase 1: Common Component Updates
The Yoda Platform team has completed the initial migration from React 16 to React 18 across the following microsites. All initial draft PRs have been created and deployed to the Core Performance Container which is on R14 release code.
 
	•	Yoda Starter Kit - Yoda Starterkit: #1224 React upgrade 18 starterkitdraft 
	•	Yoda App Shell - react 18 upgrade - app shell
	•	Yoda Site Components - React upgrade 18 site components - Draft version - do not merge
	•	Yoda-Interfaces - initial set of R18 upgrade changes - interfaces
	•	Yoda-Core-Components - initial set of r18 changes
	•	Yoda-Microsite-Common (yoda-fragment) - Pending
	•	Yoda-Account-Components - initial version of react 18 changes - account components
	•	Yoda-Checkout-Components - initial version of react 18 changes - checkout components
	•	Yoda-mini-pdp - R18 upgrade initial changes - mini pdp
TOF Microsites
	•	yoda-microsite-gallery - react 18 changes - gallery
	•	yoda-microsite-PDP - react 18 upgrade - pdp
	•	yoda-microsite-home - react 18 upgrade changes - home
	•	yoda-microsite-coupon - initial r18 changes - coupon
	•	yoda-microsite-marketing - React upgrade 18 - Marketing - draft version
BOF Microsites
	•	yoda-microsite-checkout - initialversion - React-18 - microsite-checkout
	•	yoda-microsite-account - initial version - React upgrade 18 - Microsoft Account
