	•	yoda-microsite-rewards - React upgrade 18 - rewards
	•	yoda-microsite-postpurchase - React upgrade 18 - post purchase
	•	yoda-microsite-car - initial version of React upgrade 18 - cart
 
Production Release Requirements
Technical Changes Required
	•	Merge R 20 release code changes in to all repos.
	•	consume react 18 changes on to Yoda-Microsite-Common (yoda-fragment) 
	•	make Lazy load component modifications Yoda-Microsite-Common (yoda-fragment) 
	•	fix code coverage in site components
	•	unit fixes and code coverage fix across all common and TOF Microsites
	•	enable unit test in starter kit and consume across all microsites 
	•	serverside content api call fix server side for home microsite
	•	dev validate all Microsites API calls happening as expected in prod
	•	QA stories across all Microsites
	•	Code review with architect team
	•	get performance measures after all changes
	•	merge code on to main release branch 
Pre-Release Checklist
Testing & Validation
	•	 Testing stories for all MicroSites
	•	 DevOps performance testing runs
	•	 Cross-microsite integration testing
DevOps Coordination
	•	Request performance benchmarking before production release
	•	Coordinate deployment sequence with infrastructure team
Risk Mitigation
	•	Performance testing validates production readiness
	•	Comprehensive test coverage across all Microsites
	•	There is no backword compatabile we cant revert 
 
